---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Web Based Tools - Sara's OSINT Resources">
  <article class="surface p-6 sm:p-10 prose prose-invert prose-violet max-w-none">
    <h1 class="gradient-text mb-8 text-5xl font-bold">Web Based Tools</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Search Engines & AI</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Various directory of search engines including AI for OSINT searching images, text, research, etc.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Archiving</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Clear and Dark resources for archiving text, images, webpages, and more.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Breach & Leak Detection</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Notifies in cases of data breaches or leaks; Alerts for PII; Compromised Data Checker; 
          IP, Domain Address, Social Media, and Keyword Monitor.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">People & Phone Search</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Listing start.me bookmarks; Darknet Search Engines via the clearnet; 
          People Search Tools for Russian and USA phone numbers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Data Resources</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          A list of resources for bookmarking; directories; archiving; forums; Russian onions; blogs; 
          data dumps/torrents; various search engines; projects/organizations; social media access; 
          books/literature; underground communities; hosting for images, text, and various document types.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Specialized Data</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Data from Business/Government; Hacked & Breached Data; Satellite, Aviation, Street/Maps, Telekom & More!
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Journalism Resources</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Resources for Journalists, Researchers, Investigators, and alike.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Literature</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Literature pertaining to Open-Source Investigations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Fact-Checking</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Fact-Checking / Bias Evaluators | Disinformation Checker on various subjects from politics, 
          news, trends, social-media, or cross-checking scam numbers, profiles, etc.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Crisis Resources</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Crisis and suicide prevention/intervention resources, numbers, guides, statistics, and more.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">OSINT Challenges</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          A rundown on an OSINT Challenge posted on LinkedIn.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Packet Analysis</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Packet analysis, visualization, etc.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Privacy & Data Deletion</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          Tools and resources for privacy protection and data deletion.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="surface p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-violet-200">Vehicle Information</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200/85">
          VIN, License Plate, Model # lookup tools.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
